1053
01:36:13,610 --> 01:36:15,813
Aigoo bikin kesal saja.

1054
01:36:15,813 --> 01:36:18,456
Kau bisa melacak lokasinya,
dasar gadis bodoh!

1055
01:36:18,480 --> 01:36:21,970
